Package com.pds.curiousmind.view.common

Class GlobalConstants

java.lang.Object
com.pds.curiousmind.view.common.GlobalConstants
public class GlobalConstants extends Object
GlobalConstants contains static configuration values, labels, dimensions, and icon paths used throughout the CuriousMind application. It serves as a centralized location for all shared constants.
